{"tid":2423022,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix 2021年原創韓劇劇照公開(包括王國前傳,寂靜的大海等共8部","createTime":"2021-02-25T15:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T05:40:21.000Z","uid":374891,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f0a7ec9a2785e1cd7978e04dc78f7dadd93dc73b","tid":2423022,"uid":374891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U3Gma0i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU3Gma0i.jpg&h=4cae0185&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h79ffrZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh79ffrZ.jpg&h=679bee34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XfLJ8M0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXfLJ8M0.jpg&h=3f40aa0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n寂靜的大海一共8集，以缺乏必需資源而成為荒蕪的未來為背景，為了回收疑問的樣品前往被拋棄在月亮之上的研究基地的精銳隊員之間的SF驚悚故事。"},{"pid":"d5f864639bb646a3cb7550dad6ad3fe0d87d2a68","tid":2423022,"uid":374891,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EvyGVs4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEvyGVs4.jpg&h=b0866d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NfbM6zL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfbM6zL.jpg&h=d66dd9c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7GVaON6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7GVaON6.jpg&h=2304a509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地獄由延相昊（釜山行、半島）執導，改編自延相昊創作的同名漫畫，講述與突然登場的地獄死者相遇的人們得到突如其來的地獄行通報後，經歷超自然現象的故事。一共6集。"},{"pid":"11049053fc8864e01fc488611247001477efeabc","tid":2423022,"uid":374891,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MW3PjU6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMW3PjU6.jpg&h=71aff1f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8gDvOOs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8gDvOOs.jpg&h=d70620eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與《李屍朝鮮》第一季第二季不同，以全智賢為中心的《李屍朝鮮：阿信傳》講述全智賢在第二季客串登場的北方女&middot;真&middot;部&middot;落後人阿信的故事和生死草的秘密，與為尋找生死草從而前往北方的李昌一行人相遇的疑問人物阿信的前傳故事，也是第二季延長線中的一個特別插曲。"},{"pid":"634097b67d15ab0dc9be328c6f5e2ea307aa0688","tid":2423022,"uid":374891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GwXDXHs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGwXDXHs.jpg&h=07fd247a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LiyjG88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLiyjG88.jpg&h=03ab41b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該片改編自人氣漫畫《D.P三伏天》，以抓逃兵的軍人為素材，講述平凡地進行服役中的二等兵&ldquo;安俊浩&rdquo;某天突然成為「軍務脫離追捕組」，在追逐逃兵的過程中所經歷的混亂青春故事。"},{"pid":"e69542e47f438c2fc5e3dc3480c4cde22359f899","tid":2423022,"uid":374891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:40:08.000Z","msg":"《魷魚遊戲》由黃東赫（奇怪的她）執導，講述人生的失敗者們參與到可獲得100億獎金的可疑模擬生存遊戲時发生的故事。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAaev2Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAaev2Y.jpg&h=614841be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FcSgKnZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFcSgKnZ.jpg&h=5bebfc27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4zhsQ20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4zhsQ20.jpg&h=fd2d1d8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20d912b4bcba3dccdf771d9256b139b6f9808dbf","tid":2423022,"uid":374891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UhwhtQm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUhwhtQm.jpg&h=c946c2a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F17wyg2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF17wyg2.jpg&h=7434b2f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《My Name》講述為了揭露與父親死亡相關的秘密，變身為組織的臥底以警察身份潛入後发生的令人窒息的覆仇故事。"},{"pid":"5d5c1cf8ad95de56534ae8e490a59148f59108b4","tid":2423022,"uid":374891,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OWVaORx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOWVaORx.jpg&h=38d6cf1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XpnHEYd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXpnHEYd.jpg&h=a433cfc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SLa94pU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSLa94pU.jpg&h=454e3b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《現在我們學校》講述喪屍病毒肆虐的一所高中裡，無路可逃的人們和想要營救他們的人們經歷了無法預測的極端狀況後發生的故事。"},{"pid":"8b2273fcd346f96751514ef4849fac0111a88252","tid":2423022,"uid":374891,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hag1VwX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHag1VwX.jpg&h=e71effff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pTvev5i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpTvev5i.jpg&h=cc438fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《Move To Heaven：我是遺物整理師》講述一間遺物整理公司，劇中李帝勳和飾演患有亞斯伯格症候群侄子的湯峻相，通過整理逝者們的遺物而展開的劇情，內心孤獨的李帝勳遇見侄子後逐漸了解人生溫暖，而許多亡者還沒說完的故事，也都藏在這些遺物中感人熱淚的故事。"},{"pid":"ff4e94814eb2ea2b18a90b58f013f78a58a0522b","tid":2423022,"uid":166220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T00:06:58.000Z","msg":"期待劉亞仁 全智賢同孔劉<br />\n今年都幾燒錢落韓劇到<br />\n依幾年有線台打殘無線台好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無線台最近好hit既都係得頂樓呢套<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687115e51eadd568fbe2d125e4d6c7db5b1859d2","tid":2423022,"uid":3172,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:05:07